Version 1.0.0.1 (2024-03-04)

- ColNames in CodonChoiceBiases and 
  CodonChoiceBiases deprecated changed to standard names.
- Multiple improvements in the domentation of functions.

Version 1.0.0.2 (2025-02-13)

- mLCMG: Bug fixed for special case of only one prime factor.
- xegaGeDecodeGeneDT:  Decoder for decoding random integer vectors as programs.
                 May fail.
- xegaGeDecodeGene:  Decoder for decoding random integer vectors as programs.
                 Guaranteed to work.
- xegaGeDecodeGeneFactory: Configuration of decoder.

